00:26:11.184 --> 00:26:14.866
Do you ever think that
you can just leave?

408
00:26:14.868 --> 00:26:16.868
Me?
Yeah.

409
00:26:16.870 --> 00:26:18.870
Can you do that?
Just leave?

410
00:26:18.872 --> 00:26:21.035
Yeah. go home.

411
00:26:23.157 --> 00:26:25.319
I signed up.

412
00:26:32.287 --> 00:26:33.967
CATHCART: Sir. I'm very sorry.
