415
00:26:38.334 --> 00:26:40.854
The enemy. sir.
Of course it was the enemy.
Which enemy?

416
00:26:40.856 --> 00:26:42.456
The Germans. sir.
Of course it was
the Germans.

417
00:26:42.458 --> 00:26:44.658
It'd hardly be the Japanese.
now. would it?

418
00:26:44.660 --> 00:26:46.100
I don't understand
the question. sir.

419
00:26:46.102 --> 00:26:47.942
